*   ## **_WOMEN'S ELIMINATION CHAMBER: BIANCA BELAIR DEF. NAOMI VS ROXANNE VS BAYLEY VS ALEXA BLISS VS LIV MORGAN_**
    

Naomi and Liv open.

Naomi eliminated by returning Jade Cargill

Bianca enters

Roxanne enters

Bayley enters

Alexa enters

Liv Morgan eliminated Bayley with her ObLIVion finish after Bayley dumped Roxanne over a top rope.

ROXANNE eliminated after finishers from Bianca and Alexa Bliss

Alexa Bliss is eliminated by Liv Morgan

Bianca finally eliminated Liv Morgan to win an opportunity against Rhea Ripley!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b4b8929f-9ec8-4d98-aead-0c005690a567/Messenger_creation_656210730175948.jpeg?format=original)

