![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/23ec9379-e24b-4bd9-a2c7-6bbdc4657a67/20250301_174536.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_UNSANCTIONED: KEVIN OWENS DEF SAMI ZAYN_**
    

INCREDIBLE match between Owens and Zayn that saw everything from barbed wire chairs to hockey sticks being used.

Kevin Owens demolished Sami Zayn in the end for the victory, as security and agents pleaded with him to end it.

Kevin tries to beat on Sami post match but Randy Orton returns!!

They brawl until Orton gets the upper hand and tries to PUNT KICK Kevin Owens. Security intercepted Orton and Kevin Owens escaped.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/09e994a0-40b9-4e1a-89db-b5ecdd306fba/Screenshot_20250301_180741.jpg?format=original) ![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b1c9cd55-97b8-4e84-ac00-bd7e0d453e6f/20250301_180721.jpg?format=original)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d8b932a8-b37d-40f9-b772-3469269a19bc/Screenshot_20250301_184301.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_MEN'S ELIMINATION CHAMBER: JOHN CENA DEF. DREW MCINTYRE VS CM PUNK VS LOGAN PAUL VS DAMIAN PRIEST VS SETH ROLLINS_**
    

Seth Rollins and Drew McIntyre are the first two in the match.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/403a1305-a61f-417b-aab3-f4eb59ec9279/20250301_185541.jpg?format=original)

DREW MCINTYRE IS ELIMINATED FIRST!!!

McIntyre takes out Priest out of anger and then Logan Paul hits a frog splash from the top of the chamber onto Priest.

Damian Priest is eliminated.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c3a39a11-67f7-4843-b7e7-856723d4fdca/20250301_185546.jpg?format=original)

Logan Paul is eliminated by CM Punk after a reversed Buckshot Lariat into a slap and a GTS

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b2f8c7fd-00f8-4363-9d38-804a99ee0356/processed_20250301_190059.jpg?format=original)

Seth Rollins is pinned after a double GTS/FU finisher from Punk and Cena.

CM PUNK and John Cena have a few minutes to themselves before Rollins stomps Punk and allows Cena to get the victory.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/df418eda-8a16-465b-ae98-60df7089a217/Messenger_creation_981708953902932.jpeg?format=original)

