*   ## **_JOHN CENA HAS TURNED HEEL!!! JOHN CENA HAS TURNED HEEL!!!!_**
    

Dwayne says the time has come for Cody to open his arms and embrace him.

He wants it all. He wants Cody's mind. His heart. And God have mercy, he NEEDS Cody's soul.

If he accepts, the American Nightmare lives forever. If he says no... The Dream dies... Again.

CODY TELLS THE ROCK TO GO FUCK HIMSELF.

THEN JOHN CENA EMBRACES CODY BEFORE KICKING HIM IN THE NUTS AND ATTACKING HIM WITH A ROLEX WATCH TO THE HEAD!!!!!

